  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Invitation to tender: water and leakage regulatory framework
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Prosperity Fund Programme in Brazil seeks a supplier with in depth knowledge of the water sector, especially in non-revenue water and regulatory framework.</p>

  </div>
</div>

